A python library that represents many-body operators as strings, e.g. "012003" for
an operator that has c-dagger on site 2, c on site 3 and a density operator on site 6.

## Running tests
Run the unittests from the directory containing the opytrators folder, using
python3 -m unittest discover

(or alternatively, use python3 -m opyrators.tests.test_operators)
